casebody.data:
Anthony PAPPAS, petitioner,
v.
Joseph LORINTZ, Individually and as Supreme Court Judge of New York, et al. No. 18-1212. Supreme Court of the United States May 20, 2019. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied. Justice SOTOMAYOR took no park in the consideration or decision of this petition.
